ed with previous years, when the BBC broadcasted every event live on its website or TV channels.\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1145, \"end\": 1148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9636448005455082, \"rank\": 0.03563971148069259, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, Discovery+ is the main rights holder for Paris 2024 and is showing every moment across the Eurosport channels in the UK from 7am to 10.30pm every day.\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1259, \"end\": 1269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0143898273433834e-21, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1335, \"end\": 1337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9964762613370199, \"rank\": 0.0035264908391144456, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Live stream: Fans can also catch the BBC coverage live online for free via the BBC Sport website and BBC iPlayer.\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1407, \"end\": 1410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9636448005455082, \"rank\": 0.03563971148069259, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1471, \"end\": 1474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.o